        <item>
            <title>2.0.3</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 20:22:18 +0200</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/oxineapp/oxine</link>
            <sparkle:version>203</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.0.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<style>body,*{font-family:-apple-system,system-ui;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5}h2{font-size:15px;margin:0 0 6px}ul{margin:0;padding-left:18px}li{margin:3px 0}code{background:rgba(127,127,127,.18);padding:1px 4px;border-radius:4px}</style><h2>Oxine 2.0.3</h2><ul><li>fix: Calendar, Location (Weather), Camera (Mirror), and now playing permissions can actually be granted now. The release build was missing the entitlements the hardened runtime needs, so the permission prompt never appeared. If a permission looks stuck, use Settings → Notch → Permissions to re-check.</li></ul>]]></description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/oxineapp/oxine/releases/download/v2.0.3/Oxine-2.0.3.zip" length="4210390" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="lqPKDybUIcnU+FKkU5sjlIt45VFrBYsACWAlc7L+6aGAO/uPQogc4YZtUSVB4gW6dZW25nrYYaeyfdTUSdcEAQ=="/>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>2.0.2</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 19:57:34 +0200</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/oxineapp/oxine</link>
            <sparkle:version>202</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.0.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<style>body,*{font-family:-apple-system,system-ui;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5}h2{font-size:15px;margin:0 0 6px}ul{margin:0;padding-left:18px}li{margin:3px 0}code{background:rgba(127,127,127,.18);padding:1px 4px;border-radius:4px}</style><h2>Oxine 2.0.2</h2><ul><li>fix: now playing now works in the released build, including system wide (browsers and other apps), not just Music and Spotify.</li><li>fix: the agent status grid stops hogging the side after a turn finishes. The tick shows briefly, then the side goes back to music. Stuck states also clear on their own if the CLI is closed.</li><li>fix: clearer agent states. The pixel &quot;?&quot; shows for a real permission prompt; the idle &quot;waiting&quot; notice no longer latches it.</li></ul>]]></description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/oxineapp/oxine/releases/download/v2.0.2/Oxine-2.0.2.zip" length="4209980" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="kEpc7iphuoZmFASHxddNDfsxPjisS2PFklJISH1EGcAgNHprbdsHeU0VaenTC0nEzEEsNisj05fRcXyktnpyAg=="/>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>2.0.1</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 19:29:48 +0200</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/oxineapp/oxine</link>
            <sparkle:version>201</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.0.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<style>body,*{font-family:-apple-system,system-ui;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5}h2{font-size:15px;margin:0 0 6px}ul{margin:0;padding-left:18px}li{margin:3px 0}code{background:rgba(127,127,127,.18);padding:1px 4px;border-radius:4px}</style><h2>Oxine 2.0.1</h2><ul><li>fix: the notch no longer jumps back to Home on its own. It stays on the tab you picked.</li><li>fix: the glanceable calendar loads much faster, and no longer asks for permission you already gave.</li><li>New: a Permissions panel in Settings (Notch) to re-check or re-ask for Calendar, Location, and Camera, handy after an update.</li><li>fix: the agent status grid no longer gets stuck on the &quot;waiting&quot; glyph after a turn finishes. (Re-install the hooks from Settings to pick this up.)</li></ul>]]></description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/oxineapp/oxine/releases/download/v2.0.1/Oxine-2.0.1.zip" length="4120533" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="46Jrz2WHOC7OklNE9p4vJV/c2s7T3X9mG2HZB4XMBoMKUjmampQMs7xkDNDP8xxrd7GlJ8ULVxmhAy2YRR5nCw=="/>
        </item>
